
Technology
1- Are you comfortable without your phone, computer or technological equipment for a day? Can you live without them? 
2- We are all in the social network, what is your favorite and most used social network in your country?
3- What do you think are the pros and cons of technology?
4- If you have a child who must have a phone, what is your rule if you are their parents?
5- Do you like to chat or make video calls on social networking?
6- How has technology changed your life?
7- Do you think technology controls and spies on us?
8- Do you think modern technology reduces or increases stress? Why?